 This page can only used for ESS deployments, and uses data generated by the `get-billing-data` command.

This dashboard can be used to analyse ECU (Elastic Consumption Unit) utilisation for one or several organisations.

(ECUs)"},{"type":"visualization","gridData":{"x":0,"y":108,"w":48,"h":31,"i":"6e93f0af-aab7-40e2-854c-9194c78d3f6f"},"panelIndex":"6e93f0af-aab7-40e2-854c-9194c78d3f6f","embeddableConfig":{"savedVis":{"id":"","title":"","description":"","type":"vega","params":{"spec":"{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega/v5.2.json",
  "data": [
    {
      "name": "rawData",
      "url": {
        "%context%": true,
        "%timefield%": "@timestamp",
        "index": "consumption-deployment",
        "body": {
          "runtime_mappings": {
            "details": {
              "type": "keyword",
              "script": {
                "source": "def category = doc['category'].value; if (category == 'dts') {emit(doc['type'].value);} else if (doc['tier'].size() != 0) {emit(doc['tier'].value);}"
              }
            }
          },
          "aggs": {
            "dimensions": {
              "multi_terms": {
                "terms": [
                  {"field": "deployment_name"},
                  {"field": "category"},
                  {"field": "details"}
                ],
                "size": 10000
              },
              "aggs": {"cost": {"sum": {"field": "cost"}}}
            }
          },
          "size": 0
        }
      },
      "format": {"property": "aggregations.dimensions.buckets"},
      "transform": [
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[0]", "as": "stk1"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[1]", "as": "stk2"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.key[2]", "as": "stk3"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "datum.cost.value", "as": "size"},
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.size != 0"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "nodes",
      "source": "rawData",
      "transform": [
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stk1+'|'+datum.stk2+'|'+datum.stk3",
          "as": "key"
        },
        {
          "type": "fold",
          "fields": ["stk1", "stk2", "stk3"],
          "as": ["stack", "grpId"]
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1' ? datum.stk1 : (datum.stack == 'stk2' ? datum.stk2 : datum.stk3)",
          "as": "sortField"
        },
        {
          "type": "stack",
          "groupby": ["stack"],
          "sort": {"field": "sortField", "order": "descending"},
          "field": "size"
        },
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "(datum.y0+datum.y1)/2", "as": "yc"},
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1' ? {\"term\": { \"deployment_name\": datum.grpId }} : (datum.stack == 'stk2' ?{\"term\": { \"category\": datum.grpId }}: {\"match_all\": {}})",
          "as": "filter"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "groups",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {
          "type": "aggregate",
          "groupby": ["stack", "grpId", "filter"],
          "fields": ["size"],
          "ops": ["sum"],
          "as": ["total"]
        },
        {
          "type": "stack",
          "groupby": ["stack"],
          "sort": {"field": "grpId", "order": "descending"},
          "field": "total"
        },
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "scale('y', datum.y0)", "as": "scaledY0"},
        {"type": "formula", "expr": "scale('y', datum.y1)", "as": "scaledY1"},
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'",
          "as": "rightLabel"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.total/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "leftNodes",
      "source": "groups",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "middleNodes",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk2'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "destinationNodes",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [{"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk3'"}]
    },
    {
      "name": "middleEdges",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk1'"},
        {
          "type": "lookup",
          "from": "middleNodes",
          "key": "key",
          "fields": ["key"],
          "values": ["y0", "y1", "yc"],
          "as": ["target_y0", "target_y1", "target_yc"]
        },
        {
          "type": "linkpath",
          "orient": "horizontal",
          "shape": "diagonal",
          "sourceY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.yc)"},
          "sourceX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk1') + bandwidth('x')"},
          "targetY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.target_yc)"},
          "targetX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk2')"}
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "range('y')[0]-scale('y', datum.size)",
          "as": "strokeWidth"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.size/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "rightEdges",
      "source": "nodes",
      "transform": [
        {"type": "filter", "expr": "datum.stack == 'stk2'"},
        {
          "type": "lookup",
          "from": "destinationNodes",
          "key": "key",
          "fields": ["key"],
          "as": ["target"]
        },
        {
          "type": "linkpath",
          "orient": "horizontal",
          "shape": "diagonal",
          "sourceY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.yc)"},
          "sourceX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk2') + bandwidth('x')"},
          "targetY": {"expr": "scale('y', datum.target.yc)"},
          "targetX": {"expr": "scale('x', 'stk3')"}
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "range('y')[0]-scale('y', datum.size)",
          "as": "strokeWidth"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "expr": "datum.size/domain('y')[1]",
          "as": "percentage"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "scales": [
    {
      "name": "x",
      "type": "band",
      "range": "width",
      "domain": ["stk1", "stk2", "stk3"],
      "paddingOuter": 0.05,
      "paddingInner": 0.95
    },
    {
      "name": "y",
      "type": "linear",
      "range": "height",
      "domain": {"data": "nodes", "field": "y1"}
    },
    {
      "name": "color",
      "type": "ordinal",
      "range": "category",
      "domain": {"data": "nodes", "field": "grpId"}
    },
    {
      "name": "stackNames",
      "type": "ordinal",
      "range": ["Deployment", "Category", "SKU"],
      "domain": ["stk1", "stk2", "stk3"]
    }
  ],
  "axes": [
    {
      "orient": "bottom",
      "scale": "x",
      "encode": {
        "labels": {
          "update": {"text": {"scale": "stackNames", "field": "value"}}
        }
      }
    },
    {"orient": "left", "scale": "y"}
  ],
  "marks": [
    {
      "type": "path",
      "name": "middleEdgesMark",
      "from": {"data": "middleEdges"},
      "clip": true,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "stroke": [
            {"scale": "color", "field": "stk1"}
          ],
          "strokeWidth": {"field": "strokeWidth"},
          "path": {"field": "path"},
          "strokeOpacity": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 || groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 0.9 : 0.3"
          },
          "zindex": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 || groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 1 : 0"
          },
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.stk1 + '  ' + datum.stk2 + '  ' + datum.stk3, price: format(datum.size, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"strokeOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "path",
      "name": "rightEdgesMark",
      "from": {"data": "rightEdges"},
      "clip": true,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "stroke": [
            {"scale": "color", "field": "stk3"}
          ],
          "strokeWidth": {"field": "strokeWidth"},
          "path": {"field": "path"},
          "strokeOpacity": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || groupHover.stk3 == datum.stk3 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 0.9 : 0.3"
          },
          "zindex": {
            "signal": "(groupHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 || groupHover.stk3 == datum.stk3 || (edgeHover.stk1 == datum.stk1 && edgeHover.stk2 == datum.stk2 && edgeHover.stk3 == datum.stk3)) ? 1 : 0"
          },
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.stk1 + '  ' + datum.stk2 + '  ' + datum.stk3, price: format(datum.size, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"strokeOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rect",
      "name": "groupMark",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "encode": {
        "enter": {
          "fill": {"scale": "color", "field": "grpId"},
          "width": {"scale": "x", "band": 1}
        },
        "update": {
          "x": {"scale": "x", "field": "stack"},
          "y": {"field": "scaledY0"},
          "y2": {"field": "scaledY1"},
          "fillOpacity": {"value": 0.6},
          "tooltip": {
            "signal": "{title: datum.grpId, price: format(datum.total, ',.2f') + ' ECU', percent: format(datum.percentage, '.1%')}"
          }
        },
        "hover": {"fillOpacity": {"value": 1}}
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "interactive": false,
      "encode": {
        "update": {
          "x": {
            "signal": "scale('x', datum.stack) + (datum.rightLabel ? bandwidth('x') + 8 : -8)"
          },
          "yc": {"signal": "(datum.scaledY0 + datum.scaledY1)/2"},
          "align": {"signal": "datum.rightLabel ? 'left' : 'right'"},
          "baseline": {"value": "middle"},
          "fontWeight": {
            "signal": "groupHover[datum.stack] == datum.grpId || edgeHover[datum.stack] == datum.grpId ? 'bold' : 'normal'"
          },
          "text": {
            "signal": "abs(datum.scaledY0-datum.scaledY1) > 13 ? datum.grpId : ''"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rect",
      "from": {"data": "groups"},
      "encode": {
        "enter": {
          "stroke": {"value": "#000"},
          "strokeWidth": {"value": 2},
          "width": {"scale": "x", "band": 1},
          "x": {"scale": "x", "field": "stack"},
          "y": {"field": "y0", "scale": "y"},
          "y2": {"field": "y1", "scale": "y"}
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "signals": [
    {
      "name": "groupClick",
      "on": [
        {
          "events": "@groupMark:click",
          "update": "kibanaAddFilter(datum.filter, 'consumption-deployment', datum.grpId)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "groupHover",
      "value": {},
      "on": [
        {
          "events": "@groupMark:mouseover",
          "update": "{stk1:datum.stack=='stk1' && datum.grpId, stk2:datum.stack=='stk2' && datum.grpId, stk3:datum.stack=='stk3' && datum.grpId}"
        },
        {"events": "mouseout", "update": "{}"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "edgeHover",
      "value": {},
      "on": [
        {
          "events": "@middleEdgesMark:mouseover",
          "update": "{stk1:datum.stk1, stk2:datum.stk2, stk3:datum.stk3}"
        },
        {
          "events": "@rightEdgesMark:mouseover",
          "update": "{stk1:datum.stk1, stk2:datum.stk2, stk3:datum.stk3}"
        },
        {"events": "mouseout", "update": "{}"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}"},"uiState":{},"data":{"aggs":[],"searchSource":{"query":{"query":"","language":"kuery"},"filter":[]}}},"enhancements":{},"hidePanelTitles":false},"title":"Costs attribution Sankey chart"}]
